### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@customerId = <pega_el_id_del_cliente>

### ─────────────────────────────
### CUSTOMERS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Crear cliente sin teléfono ni dirección (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VyX2lkIjoiNjQ0MjJhODEtNTNhNi00NmMwLWJiYTEtNTY0NzllYjg5NGFjIiwiZW1haWwiOiJhZG1pbkBhZG1pbi5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJleHAiOjE3ODE1NDI4NDMsImlhdCI6MTc4MTQ1NjQ0M30.qClA-gz8vmXJ1bHUwrzOcu-CTsF9t2sMm0Wc8VX-i68

{
  "name": "Cliente Nuevo",
  "type": "COMPANY",
  "phone": "2804207744",
  "address": "Ruta 4"
}

###

### Crear cliente (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Aluar",
  "type": "COMPANY",
  "phone": "111222333",
  "address": "Av. Corrientes 123, CABA"
}

###

### Crear cliente persona (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "type": "PERSON",
  "phone": "444555666",
  "address": "Calle Falsa 456"
}

###

